121
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:45,480
Um and and we could have admitted the point of diminishing returns and it just doesn't matter.

122
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:54,120
And I I think in many cases people will add a feature, it's not good enough, um and so people don't use it or appreciate it,

123
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:58,760
