00:33:08,000 --> 00:33:11,880
That becomes really critical and I think very very few people recognize that.

433
00:33:11,880 --> 00:33:17,480
They're like I want to get people who come to my web page to the sign-up form as quickly as possible.

434
00:33:17,480 --> 00:33:21,040
But if they don't know what they're signing up for, they don't know what it's going to do after,

435
00:33:21,040 --> 00:33:22,480
is it going to spam them?

436
00:33:22,480 --> 00:33:27,440
Um They don't know am I going to have to pay on the next step or or what?

437
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:29,840
Then they're just going to back out.

438
00:33:29,840 --> 00:33:39,960
And this was like a a lifelong battle because the remove friction um kind of orientation is so deep in people.

439
00:33:39,960 --> 00:33:46,400
Again, it really makes a difference in in those cases where people do have an intent and they do know what they're trying to do.

