445
00:34:20,080 --> 00:34:27,840
And I think that the trick is for most of the unique parts of any application, most of like the specific things that your app,

446
00:34:27,840 --> 00:34:34,520
your product, your software does are areas where the challenge is going to be comprehension instead of friction.

